parameters: The monsters are taken care of. That should do it.

I was worried I might have gotten rusty from all the
hesitation.

Once I've decided on something, I don't waver halfway
through.
Even if it's a wicked promise with you.

Well, as long as you're hunting monsters for me, it's all
good.
So, shall we collect the materials and head back to town?
To town? Not to your house?
Yeah, yeah, there's something I've been thinking about.

Let's not go straight home but meet up at a certain place in
town instead.

I don't quite get it, but I suppose I have no choice but to
go along.
